00:19:23.260 --> 00:19:24.820
It was born in Iraq.

00:19:24.820 --> 00:19:27.520
And when the Syrian Civil
War really got going,

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:29.020
they saw an opportunity.

00:19:29.020 --> 00:19:35.560
They migrated into Syria, took
territory, came back into Iraq

00:19:35.560 --> 00:19:37.930
and overran, I think,
five Iraqi Army divisions,

00:19:37.930 --> 00:19:39.850
then took all their weapons.

00:19:39.850 --> 00:19:44.140
And they just started sort
of bouncing back and forth

00:19:44.140 --> 00:19:47.590
between Syria and Iraq, grabbing
more and more territory,

00:19:47.590 --> 00:19:52.500
taking over oil fields,
creating oil revenue, tens,

00:19:52.500 --> 00:19:54.250
hundreds of millions
of dollars of revenue

00:19:54.250 --> 00:19:56.120
now being generated
by this machine,

00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:59.170
which could then pay for
more arms and more jihadis.

00:19:59.170 --> 00:20:01.000
The whole thing
sort of snowballed.

00:20:01.000 --> 00:20:03.820
And it wasn't until
recently that ground forces

00:20:03.820 --> 00:20:06.770
were able to start
to roll that back.

