00:34:26.730 --> 00:34:30.389
And I guess we're
working with the Kurds

00:34:30.389 --> 00:34:32.360
to a degree or something.

00:34:32.360 --> 00:34:33.989
Do you see US
involvement increasing?

00:34:33.989 --> 00:34:36.072
We're going to have more
soldiers as time goes on?

00:34:36.072 --> 00:34:39.000
SEBASTIAN JUNGER: Yeah, there's
a Marine expeditionary unit

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:39.760
there.

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:44.280
There's a bunch of 155s over
there, artillery over there.

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:47.670
They've got aircraft flying
out of Northern Iraq I guess.

00:34:47.670 --> 00:34:49.800
I don't really know
the tactical details,

00:34:49.800 --> 00:34:51.929
but yeah, there are
US forces over there.

00:34:51.929 --> 00:34:53.555
They're focused
on defeating ISIS.

00:34:53.555 --> 00:34:54.929
I don't know
exactly what they're

00:34:54.929 --> 00:35:00.060
going to do when ISIS is
gone and different militia

00:35:00.060 --> 00:35:02.520
groups that they were allied
with, including the Kurds,

00:35:02.520 --> 00:35:04.770
start fighting with each
other to control the areas

00:35:04.770 --> 00:35:09.300
that ISIS used to occupy,
particularly the oilfields.

00:35:09.300 --> 00:35:15.750
So are US forces then going
to become peacekeeping forces?

00:35:15.750 --> 00:35:17.710
I'm not sure exactly
what's going to happen.

00:35:17.710 --> 00:35:19.251
I'm not sure the
administration knows

00:35:19.251 --> 00:35:21.870
exactly what's going
to happen if Turkey

00:35:21.870 --> 00:35:29.670
decides that parts of those
areas really should be Turkey.

00:35:29.670 --> 00:35:32.120
They feel that Mosul
is a Turkish city.

00:35:32.120 --> 00:35:33.170
Mosul's in Northern Iraq.

00:35:36.130 --> 00:35:37.800
How's that going to go?

00:35:37.800 --> 00:35:43.680
There's an expeditionary unit
in between Turkey and Mosul.

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:46.530
It's going to have to stay
there to keep Turkey from trying

00:35:46.530 --> 00:35:48.480
to claim a piece of--

00:35:48.480 --> 00:35:51.750
I mean, it's a huge mess.

00:35:51.750 --> 00:35:55.560
And the administration right
now, the Trump administration

00:35:55.560 --> 00:36:00.330
is juggling an awful lot of
very complicated situations.

00:36:00.330 --> 00:36:02.520
I hope they have the
bandwidth to figure out

00:36:02.520 --> 00:36:06.700
a wise course of action, a
wise strategy in that area.

00:36:06.700 --> 00:36:07.690
I hope they do.

00:36:07.690 --> 00:36:09.450
I wouldn't say it's
likely that they do,

00:36:09.450 --> 00:36:12.210
but I hope they do,
I mean for our sake

00:36:12.210 --> 00:36:14.050
and for the sake of
the people over there.

00:36:14.050 --> 00:36:16.819
There's a lot of innocent people
still stuck in that country.

00:36:16.819 --> 00:36:18.360
They really don't
need Western powers

00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:21.740
making more mistakes
with that area.

